                  "pageId": 1583857,
                  "revisionId": 2699529,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Yareli will lose her immunity to stagger status effects from enemy targets (such as Knockdown); however she will still be immune from self-inflicted stagger by weapons she uses. It's unclear if this is intentional or not, as riding Merulina normally provides complete status immunity, including knockdown immunity from enemies."
