                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Loyal Merulina's Sea Snares inherits the duration, range, damage per second, damage increase per second, and damage vulnerability stats of Yareli's own Sea Snares. This is still the case even if Yareli's Sea Snares ability is overridden by another Helminth ability."
